def eval_model(ytest,ypred):
    cm = confusion_matrix(ytest,ypred)
    print(cm)
    print(classification_report(ytest,ypred))
def mscore(model):
    print('Train Score',model.score(x_train,y_train))
    print ('Test Score',model.score(x_test,y_test))
